{"type":"message","id":"0ebb9799","parentId":"ee5c62ac","timestamp":"2026-04-01T22:05:14.537Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The learning note has been saved. Let me also check if the file exists and has content.","thinkingSignature":"5ed037ab5569f2798d698ed8a8d96cac39484f9e35b8b25faec3d8f66cc26d0d"},{"type":"text","text":"自主学习完成 ✅\n\n已保存至 `/home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/memory/学习笔记.md`，涵盖三大领域的关键信息：\n\n1. **企业数字化转型**：200亿专项补贴政策（2026-2028）、工业数据筑基行动、汽车行业专项方案、地方转型目标\n2. **智能安防**：AI从被动到主动决策、边缘计算下沉、数字孪生、市场规模3500亿美元、芯片涨价带来格局变化\n3. **IT运维**：AIOps 3.0实现故障全流程自主化、运维从后台到业务增长引擎、外包服务升级洗牌、人才哑铃型结构\n\n已附上对道简网络的战略启示与行动建议。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":4503,"output":169,"cacheRead":43981,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":48653,"cost":{"input":0.0013509,"output":0.0002028,"cacheRead":0.00131943,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0028731299999999998}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775081108879}}
